Package jp.digitalmuseum.jogl

Class Summary
JoglCoordinates Default coordinate system.
JoglCoordinates_ARToolKit Coordinate system suitable for use with ARToolKit.
JoglModel Base class for holding a three-dimensional model object for JOGL.
JoglModel.Color Class for holding color parameter.
JoglModel.FloatArray Class for holding a float array.
JoglModel.JoglMaterial Class which represents a JOGL material.
JoglModel.JoglObject Class which represents a JOGL object.
JoglModel.LightSourcePoint Class for holding three-dimensional coordinates of a light source.
JoglModel.Point Class for holding three-dimensional coordinates of a point.
JoglModel.UV Class for holding UV texture mapping parameters.
JoglModelMqo Metasequoia 3D model file (*.mqo) loader for Java OpenGL (JOGL.)
JoglTextureManager Class for managing textures of JoglModel.
JoglTextureManager.Tga Class for loading TGA image file.
